item.title: Home Remodeling
item.dc:creator: davinci
item.content:encoded:
[vc_row][vc_column][qk_service title="Design and Build" image="562"]At Affordable Contractor Services, we provide you a service for all your design and construction needs. Saving you time and money while making sure the project is done correctly. We not only build home additions, we create living spaces that renew peoples pride in owning a home. Whether you hire us to put on a extra room, extended garage, a second story, an enlarge or remodeled kitchen or bathroom, or even build a patio or deck, Affordable Contractor Services creates a highly detailed design plan and goes over those details with each client before any ground is broken. For a project that is finished on time and to the homeowners total satisfaction, call us today. We are a full service licensed and bonded contractor that specialized in home remodels and improvements. Remodeling your home can increase its value and improve comfort, style, and function for your family. We strive to ensure that every detail in your project plan or dream is captured from start to finish without missing any details. These services could include and involve removing load bearing walls, rearranging rooms and home layouts, adding entire additions to existing structures, room remodeling and more. We communicate often and openly with all of our clients in the hopes of truly understanding their wants and needs as no two homes are the same. In our experience, this always yields higher-quality additions, faster project turnaround times, and a happier customer. Consult with Affordable Contractor Services to plan and budget for each phase and aspect of your renovation. [/qk_service][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width="1/2"][vc_wp_text]

item.title: Sample Page
item.dc:creator: davinci
item.content:encoded:
This is an example page. It's different from a blog post because it will stay in one place and will show up in your site navigation (in most themes). Most people start with an About page that introduces them to potential site visitors. It might say something like this:
Hi there! I'm a bike messenger by day, aspiring actor by night, and this is my website. I live in Los Angeles, have a great dog named Jack, and I like piña coladas. (And gettin' caught in the rain.)
...or something like this:
The XYZ Doohickey Company was founded in 1971, and has been providing quality doohickeys to the public ever since. Located in Gotham City, XYZ employs over 2,000 people and does all kinds of awesome things for the Gotham community.
As a new WordPress user, you should go to your dashboard to delete this page and create new pages for your content. Have fun!

Cabinets can make or break your home. You store everything in cabinets in the kitchen and bathroom and are a aesthetic that is often underappreciated. Affordable Contractor Services understands that cabinets and counter tops are integral part of any home an want to help you realize your dream home. We place performance, quality and reliability above all else and "Our Designers" will work with you to craft one of a kind layout that is tailored to your specific needs. No matter what type of cabinets or counters you are looking for, Affordable Contractor Services can help you achieve your dreams on time and on budget. [/vc_column_text]

Building basements, garages, driveways, new foundations all require concrete and at Affordable Contractor Services we understand that it is important to have quality workmanship on any concrete job. With our Team we guarantee the highest quality of work when dealing with cement and concrete and our jobs will be done on time and on an affordable budget.   [/vc_column_text]

item.title: Residential siding replacement job in Hazel Dell
item.dc:creator: Bryon
item.content:encoded: This is a residential house in hazel Dell. It had cedar lap siding that was damaged. The customer requested it to be replaced. we replaced two walls and some minor siding in other areas. It took three days to complete.

item.title: Welcome to Affordable Contractor Services
item.dc:creator: davinci
item.content:encoded: Our Crew at Affordable Contractor Services has been working in the construction Industry for over 20 years. Noticing a need in the field Byron decided to go out on his own and provide quality work at affordable prices for everyone. We appreciate your interest and your business and will treat any job that comes our way as if we are working on our own projects. Affordable Contractor Services holds itself to the highest standards and you will receive only the best Quality, Customer Satisfaction, Dedication and Prices that can be found.

item.title: Interior Remodeling
item.dc:creator: davinci
item.content:encoded:
Interior to go with your Dreams

Your home is very important to you. The flooring, ceilings, windows, rooms and everything else that is inside should match up to your vision of your home. Our team of designers will work with you to make that kitchen, bathroom, living room or whatever else you are looking to do become what you dream of. At Affordable Contractor Services we pride ourselves in making your dreams a reality on an affordable budget. Schedule an In Home Consultation Today

item.title: Home Additions
item.dc:creator: davinci
item.content:encoded:
Expand Your Dreams

Need more room in your home? Whether it is a second story addition, a basement conversion or a expansion to add on to your current home, Affordable Contractor Services is here to help. Affordable Contractor Services will help you create a "new" home by adding to your existing house. From planning out where and how build your addition to the unveiling of the project, our team is here to assist in making your home like new again. Schedule an In Home Consultation Today

item.title: Custom Cabinets
item.dc:creator: davinci
item.content:encoded: At Affordable Contractor Services we place performance quality and reliability above all else. Our designers will work alongside with you to craft a one-of-a-kind cabinetry layout that is tailored to your family's specific needs. We also offer our customers a vast variety of cabinets from all the leading manufactures. No matter what type of cabinetry you're searching for, Affordable Contractor Services is your one stop shop. Schedule an In Home Consultation Today

item.title: Exterior Remodeling
item.dc:creator: davinci
item.content:encoded:
Maintain Your Dreams

Our Exterior Remodeling and home services include repair, installation, cleaning, replacement and more! The outside of your house is often the first impression of your personal style and household. Maintaining the exterior of your home and its structural integrity can also prevent more costly repairs in the long run. From painting, roofing, gutter cleaning, concrete work to siding repair and more, Affordable Contractor Services is the best choice for Vancouver and the outlining areas. Whether you need something custom built or a store-bought product installed, we deliver a guaranteed satisfaction for all of your outdoor project needs no matter how small or big the job might be. We are the one-stop solution for all of your exterior home projects. Schedule an In Home Consultation Today

item.title: Bathroom Remodeling
item.dc:creator: davinci
item.content:encoded:
Create your own Personal Bathroom

At Affordable Contractor Services, we offer different levels of a bathroom remodels. This includes cosmetic, pull and replace, and custom. We can create the bathroom of your dreams - on time and on budget. Ifyou need outlets, faucets, toilets, tubs, shower-heads, venting fans, or whatever the project is that you need completed for you bathroom remodel, we promise to arrive on time and perform quality workmanship that's guaranteed to your satisfaction. Affordable Contractor Services is the one-stop solution to your bathroom and remodeling project needs. Schedule an In Home Consultation Today

item.title: Drywall
item.dc:creator: davinci
item.content:encoded:
Drywall is one of those things you really dont notice in a home unless its done wrong!
Thats why its important to hire a professional you can trust for all of your drywall repair and installation needs like Affordable Contractor Services. Whether you want to replace a damaged area with matching texture or start fresh, Affordable Contractor Services is your resource for reliable drywall installation, patching and replacement work.
Our work is performed by an experienced who will walk you through every step of the process for a simple and seamless experience. Our goal is your complete satisfaction.

item.title: Gates and Fencing
item.dc:creator: davinci
item.content:encoded:
We offer premier fencing and gate installation in the Vancouver area with the some best wood and vinyl products to last for years!
If not sure which style of fence is right for you, or you like multiple different styles and elements from several types of fences? Then call us today to create a one of a kind fence perfectly suited to your needs and wants.
We offer Wood fencing that adds security and beauty with a wide range of styles to compliment your home. Vinyl fencing is also availability in verity of styles and colors. Call today and speak with a specialist here at Affordable Contractor Services to compare the differences to see what best fits your needs.

item.title: Decking
item.dc:creator: davinci
item.content:encoded:
Decks can give your home that beauty like no other while added a spacious area as well as increase your homes value!
A deck can holds its value over time and we can install tradition wood or composite for that extension to your yard. Either way it gives you a beautiful look outside deck to your enjoyment.
We are a full service Handyman and Contractor company with a focus on excellence and we can help you with all phases of your deck, railing, patio cover or other outdoor structure projects.

item.title: Deck and Patio Covers
item.dc:creator: davinci
item.content:encoded:
Is Deck too hot and you need a shade solutions for your deck or patioa? Well, you need a patio or deck cover to keep your deck cooler and screen out harmful ultraviolet rays.
Affordable Contractor Services designs and builds those beautiful Deck or Patio covers over that concrete pad or that wood/composite deck on the rear of a residence. These deck covers could be very difficult to build, but not with Affordable Contractor Services. We can deliver that perfect patio and deck cover for you.
Just call us today for an estimate.

item.title: Window Installation
item.dc:creator: davinci
item.content:encoded:
So, when it comes time to assess your job, we take extra special care to ensure that the job is done right the first time.
Affordable Contractor Services can remove the old windows and install the new ones with easy. However, there maybe other work or items needed to make the installation smooth for those special new windows. Especially if the new windows are brand-new for the home. We will consult with you as every house is unique, so we want to make sure that your windows will meet your exact needs as we are dedicated to keeping our clients happy with Affordable Contractor Services.

item.title: Shelving
item.dc:creator: davinci
item.content:encoded:
Adding shelving can increase your storage capacity area while adding beauty and value to your home & more.
It can be difficult to find a location around your home to store all of those items you might haveand even more difficult to find a way that looks aesthetically pleasing to your home. Not only can we install shelving you might have bought in a store, but can custom build something to your specifications. If you are considering increasing the storage and look of your home with custom shelves or bookcases or other woodwork, you should not hesitate to contact Affordable Contractor Services today.

item.title: Painting
item.dc:creator: davinci
item.content:encoded:
Our mission here at Affordable Contractor Services is to deliver a detailed and professional service that you expect and deserve.
Whether youre repainting the entire room or just updating wall inside or out, we have you covered. A fresh coat of paint can breathe life back into any room, or exterior of your house. Whether you have an indoor or outdoor paint job, the professionals at Affordable Contractor Services can help fulfill your needs. We know what it takes to makes a great paint job that you could be proud of.

item.title: Door Installation
item.dc:creator: davinci
item.content:encoded:
We have many different door options for you including patio doors, sliding glass doors, pocket-sliding doors, French in-swing or out-swing, stacking glass doors, fiberglass doors, wood doors and more!
Whether you need a beautiful front entryway door or a magnificent patio door, Affordable Contractor Services is that professional exterior door installation service that you need. We will assess your job needs, show you different options that you might not have thought of and give you option that we can provide through the manufacturers in order to get started on installing that dream door of yours.

item.title: Garden and Tool Sheds
item.dc:creator: davinci
item.content:encoded:
Running out of space to put your garden supplies, lawnmower and tools? Then a Garden or Tool Shed maybe just the thing you need.
For most homeowners, adding that tool shed or garden shed for storage is at the top of their to-do list. Would your like to cross it off your list and add it to ours? That way, you dont have to worry about the time it will take to finish it in order to have that proper area to store your tools and equipment. Let Affordable Contractor Services do the heavy lifting on your behalf when it comes to adding a garden and tool sheds you're looking for.

item.title: Kitchen Remodeling
item.dc:creator: davinci
item.content:encoded: Thinking about remodeling your kitchen?Looking for kitchen design ideas? Our team can bring your vision to life. Your kitchen is more then likely the heart of your home and we can help make your dream kitchen a reality! Whether repairing a leaky faucet, installing new cabinets, or adding that finishing touch to your kitchen, we are equipped to handle that major or minor project in your kitchen. Our dependable and experienced services will create that perfect kitchen of you. We can create the kitchen of your dreams - on time and on budget. Schedule an In Home Consultation Today

item.title: Evergreen Highlands Window Replacement
item.dc:creator: davinci
item.content:encoded: Affordable Contractor Services replaced a basement window that was not energy efficient. It was a wood panel single pane window that was replaced with a Vinyl Picture window frame, EC Argon glass which brought his U-Value down to .26 which is above normal.[gallery size="medium" link="file" ids="901,903,902"]

item.title: Burton/Evergreen Siding Repair
item.dc:creator: davinci
item.content:encoded: Affordable Contractor services was contacted to help repair a siding on job 2 sides of a home in the Burton/Evergreen neighborhood in Vancouver WA. The siding was faded, the bottom had dry rot, and needed to be replaced. Put on new siding, re graveled around the edge of the house and painted the 2 sides. [gallery size="medium" link="file" ids="948,949,947,946,945,944"]

item.title: Interior Trim Update in Fircrest
item.dc:creator: davinci
item.content:encoded: Affordable Contractor Services was contracted to finish installing trim on the interior of a home in the Fircrest neighborhood in Vancouver WA. The kitchen, dinning room living room and hallway wad done in a Craftsman style of Trim that required a finish carpenter then caulked and painted the Trim. [gallery size="medium" link="file" ids="891,895,899,897,896"]

item.title: Fence Replacement in Felida
item.dc:creator: davinci
item.content:encoded: Affordable Contractor Services replaced a fence that was old, rotten, and faded in the Felida neighborhood in Vancouver WA. Over 200ft of fence was needing to be replaced overall and we used #2 Gram Cedar Fencing from Parr Lumbar. The entire job including clean up took 3 days. [gallery size="medium" link="file" ids="906,907,916,908,909,910,911,913,914"]
